To add a new plugin:

  git submodule add <repository>

To update after a fresh checkout:

  git submodule init
  git submodule update

Current list:

  command-t             file navigation via <Leader>t
    to compile extension: cd command-t/ruby/command-t; ruby extconf.rb; make
  IndentConsistencyCop  check indentation consistency
  jedi-vim              Python autocompletion
    in jedi-vim run: git submodule update --init
  vim-surround          surround things with parentheses/quotes/etc.
  vimtips-fortune       show tips on startup

